# Frontend (pointer)

Canonical guidance: `@rules/nextjs.mdc`.

Use **@nextjs** (and referenced rules) for App Router, React, and styling. For non-Next frontends: `@rules/javascript.mdc` (Vue, Svelte, HTMX, Shopify theme). For Bootstrap-based styling: `@rules/styling/bootstrap.mdc`.
